      "values": ["On Computable Numbers, with an Application to the Entscheidungsproblem", "The Applications of Probability to Cryptography", "Paper on Statistics of Repetitions", "The Chemical Basis of Morphogenesis", "Nova PBS纪录片《解码纳粹秘密》", "艾伦·图灵选集"]
    },
    {
